1、parameter check
2、main part
（1）n integer times larger：
     a.copy one pixel to n* n
        1st.prepare the larger bmp frame:header,pixels(),padding
        2nd.no padding:for n hight,for n width
     b.deal with padding
     c.change header：
        BITMAPFILEHEADER:bfSize
        BITMAPINFOHEADER:biWidth
（3）n between 0 to 1:
     a.support 0.01
     b.how to round
     c.define the lower edge,3*3.if smaller than this cannot do,just to 3*3
     d.


（4）n larger than 1 and is float

